Path: godot/classes/class_joint2d.rst
Summary: Abstract base class for all 2D physics joints in Godot.

Inherits: Node2D < CanvasItem < Node < Object
Inherited By: DampedSpringJoint2D, GrooveJoint2D, PinJoint2D

Abstract base class for all 2D physics joints. Provides common functionality for connecting and constraining physics bodies in 2D space. All specific joint types (like PinJoint2D and DampedSpringJoint2D) inherit from this class to implement their unique constraint behaviors.
---CHUNK---
Document: Joint2D
Path: godot/classes/class_joint2d.rst
Summary: Abstract base class for 2D physics joints that bind two physics bodies and apply constraints.

Abstract base class for all joints in 2D physics. 2D joints bind together two physics bodies (node_a and node_b) and apply a constraint.
